        <p>If you want to share your knowledge and help others, mentorship will make you happy. Become a mentor now.</p>
        <%= link_to "Join as a mentor", new_expert_path, class:"btn btn-danger" %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
          <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i>
          <i class="fa fa-money fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
        </span>
